                  <decoDesc>
                    <summary>(in the style of the Ground Hornbill painter). Compare the first miniature with EMIP 118/Weiner 27, f. ii v(erso). The style of this artwork and the pose is very reminiscent of the ground hornbill painter’s work as seen in Bodleian MS. Aeth. e. 28, f. 1v (see Demeke and Delamarter, Plate 9, p. 148). The same can be said for the subsequent pages with geometric patterns around the text</summary>
